01:02.936 --> 01:04.727
but we gotta check inside
just to make sure.

01:04.738 --> 01:05.760
All right.

01:21.910 --> 01:23.114
Right, now.

01:34.136 --> 01:35.830
Is that coming from upstairs?

01:35.831 --> 01:36.862
I hear voices.

01:36.941 --> 01:38.117
Sounds like a radio.

01:44.995 --> 01:46.208
Better check upstairs.

01:46.209 --> 01:47.209
Oh, my God.

01:47.590 --> 01:49.791
That's what's-his-name from the radio.

01:50.721 --> 01:51.721
Max Hudson.

01:52.222 --> 01:54.163
A gas leak at Max Hudson's house?

01:54.175 --> 01:55.950
Oh, he's gonna have
a field day with this!

02:02.391 --> 02:03.439
<i>Tell me, Kimberly,</i>

02:03.440 --> 02:05.825
<i>that you actually believe
in the sanctity of marriage.</i>

02:05.897 --> 02:06.913
<i>I do.</i>

02:06.947 --> 02:08.768
<i>Kimberly can't even spell "sanctity."</i>

02:08.957 --> 02:09.966
I'll turn the gas off.

02:09.967 --> 02:10.967
<i>Say sanctity.</i>

02:11.316 --> 02:12.321
<i>Santity.</i>

02:12.322 --> 02:13.322
<i>Close enough!</i>

02:14.227 --> 02:15.227
<i>Close enough!</i>

02:16.010 --> 02:17.577
<i>We have a winner!</i>

02:22.483 --> 02:24.441
Hey, Max.
There's a cop on line one.

02:24.442 --> 02:25.794
He says it's important.

02:27.247 --> 02:28.247
Okay, uh...

02:28.462 --> 02:30.278
I'll just take it in the back,
all right?

02:30.312 --> 02:31.450
Anybody you know?

02:38.344 --> 02:39.814
My God, is she all right?

02:40.946 --> 02:41.996
Oh, my God...

02:42.403 --> 02:43.997
Is she all right?
Oh, my God.

02:48.112 --> 02:49.112
Speaking.

02:51.464 --> 02:52.464
My wife...?

02:53.964 --> 02:55.669
Oh, my God, is she all right?

02:58.223 --> 02:59.223
Yes, sir.

03:00.473 --> 03:02.240
I- I understand.
I'll be right there.

